label: SplashHome
text: This application is intended for the comparison of flow capacity provided for pipes of various shapes and sizes for a specified slope and appropriate roughness coefficient. Actual flow rates are dependent upon additional contributing factors such as entrance losses and culvert length not addressed by this application. Hydraulic Capacity of Culvert
